      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813129,
      "updated": 1542813139
    },
    {
      "id": "617175b4aff09e0000334fe0",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/c87874588e271a962ef3a9fd33e0a404]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1634825652,
      "updated": 1634825656
    },
    {
      "id": "617175b9aff09e0000334fe2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1634825657,
      "updated": 1634825657
    },
    {
      "id": "617175b4aff09e0000334fe1",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1634825652,
      "updated": 1634825654
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf575d5aff09e0000105800",
      "text": "[知識の獲得戦略]と[スペシャリスト]・[ジェネラリスト]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813142,
      "updated": 1542813160
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57a27aff09e0000105827",
      "text": "僕がよく使う[知識の分布図]をコードで生み出して実験ができるようにしようと考えた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542814248,
      "updated": 1542814274
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57a41aff09e0000105828",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542814274,
      "updated": 1542814274
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57659aff09e0000105818",
      "text": "毎ステップ3つの学習対象の選択肢が与えられて、自分の知識獲得戦略に従って一つを学ぶ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813273,
      "updated": 1542813391
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57671aff09e0000105819",
      "text": "学ぶとランダムな量の知識が得られる。得られる知識領域にもランダムなノイズを加えているので、「学ぼうとしたことのちょっとずれた分野の知識を得る」こともある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813297,
      "updated": 1542814166
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57719aff09e000010581b",
      "text": "知識獲得戦略以外の条件を同じにして、3つの選択肢の中から「自分がもっとの知識の多い対象」を選ぶ戦略(スペシャリスト戦略)と、「自分がもっとの知識の少ない対象」を選ぶ戦略(ジェネラリスト戦略)で場合でどういう差が出るかを観察した。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813466,
      "updated": 1542813538
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf575ccaff09e00001057fe",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/45da70185788ef347932cb3983a11a15]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813132,
      "updated": 1542813135
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57764aff09e000010581c",
      "text": "スペシャリストに対してピークが一つだけのようなイメージを持っていたが、複数のピークが発生した。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813541,
      "updated": 1542813623
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57808aff09e000010581e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813704,
      "updated": 1542813704
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57808aff09e000010581f",
      "text": "もっと「大部分の領域でジェネラリストが勝つが、スペシャリストは自分の得意分野でだけ圧倒的に強い」という現象を想像していたが、44%の領域でスペシャリストが勝つ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813704,
      "updated": 1542813750
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57764aff09e000010581d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813541,
      "updated": 1542813541
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf578c1aff09e0000105820",
      "text": "この振る舞いは、全部で100ある学習対象のうち、ランダムな3つの選択肢から選ぶという「学びの対象の自由度」が乏しい状況だから起こることである。与えられる選択肢を10個にするとこうなる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813889,
      "updated": 1542815036
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf578f9aff09e0000105822",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/c87874588e271a962ef3a9fd33e0a404]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813946,
      "updated": 1542813961
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57908aff09e0000105823",
      "text": "選択肢を30、つまり全対象の3割から自由に選べるようにするとこうなる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813961,
      "updated": 1542814021
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57945aff09e0000105824",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/bb6f9c91f74d4cbb9931912a82923f2d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542814021,
      "updated": 1542814023
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57caeaff09e000010582f",
      "text": "自分の一番得意なものを選択する「スペシャリスト戦略」は、選択の自由度が高まるほど一つのピークに集中するようになる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542814895,
      "updated": 1542814923
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57947aff09e0000105825",
      "text": "一方、ジェネラリスト戦略は選択の自由度にあまり影響されていない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542814023,
      "updated": 1542814926
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf578c1aff09e0000105821",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813889,
      "updated": 1542813889
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57beeaff09e0000105829",
      "text": "3人のスペシャリストと1人のジェネラリスト",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542814702,
      "updated": 1542814735
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57c18aff09e000010582d",
      "text": "ジェネラリストは誰も似ているので3人集めても文殊の知恵にならないが、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542814745,
      "updated": 1542814757
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57c26aff09e000010582e",
      "text": "スペシャリストが集まって自分の強みを発揮すると大部分の領域でジェネラリストの集団より高い知識を発揮するようになる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542814758,
      "updated": 1542814813
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57bf6aff09e000010582b",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/2cae28889415e54e823d6c1caf5a83be]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542814711,
      "updated": 1542814714
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57bf9aff09e000010582c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542814714,
      "updated": 1542814714
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57beeaff09e000010582a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542814702,
      "updated": 1542814702
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf575cfaff09e00001057ff",
      "text": "[Colab https://colab.research.google.com/drive/15or2hCehfO-NfWFjX5WBeKCS0vOc55bI]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813135,
      "updated": 1542813229
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57624aff09e0000105802",
      "text": "code:python",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813221,
      "updated": 1542813236
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57634aff09e0000105804",
      "text": " import numpy as np",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813236,
      "updated": 1542813253
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57645aff09e0000105805",
      "text": " from matplotlib import pyplot as plt",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813253,
      "updated": 1542813253
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57645aff09e0000105806",
      "text": " KNOWLEDGE_WIDTH = 100",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813254,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e0000105807",
      "text": " TIMES = 10000",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e0000105808",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e0000105809",
      "text": " def get_knowledge(policy):",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e000010580a",
      "text": "   knowledge = np.zeros(KNOWLEDGE_WIDTH)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e000010580b",
      "text": "   for t in range(TIMES):",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e000010580c",
      "text": "     targets = np.random.randint(0, KNOWLEDGE_WIDTH, size=3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e000010580d",
      "text": "     target = targets[policy(knowledge[targets])]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e000010580e",
      "text": "     target = int(np.random.normal(target))",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e000010580f",
      "text": "     if target < 0 or target >= KNOWLEDGE_WIDTH: continue",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e0000105810",
      "text": "     knowledge[target] += np.random.random()",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e0000105811",
      "text": "   return knowledge",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e0000105812",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e0000105813",
      "text": " specialist = get_knowledge(policy=lambda xs: xs.argmax())",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e0000105814",
      "text": " generalist = get_knowledge(policy=lambda xs: xs.argmin())",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e0000105815",
      "text": " plt.plot(specialist, label=\"specialist\")",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e0000105816",
      "text": " plt.plot(generalist, label=\"generalist\")",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
    {
      "id": "5bf57650aff09e0000105817",
      "text": " plt.legend()",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1542813264,
      "updated": 1542813264
    },
